    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint condition. The exterior paint and body are flawless with no scratches, dents, or chips. The interior is in pristine condition with no signs of wear on the upholstery, dashboard, or carpets. All mechanical and electronic systems function perfectly.",
      "price": 49000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few small door dings, and the clear coat is starting to fade on the roof. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely need a suspension tune-up soon as there is some minor rattling over bumps. The interior is intact but shows significant wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the carpets. It\u2019s a solid, functional vehicle for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience the perfect synergy of refined performance and long-term reliability. This vehicle has been maintained to an exacting standard, presenting in impressive condition that reflects true pride of ownership. From its responsive handling to its clean, sophisticated interior, every aspect of this car has been vetted to ensure it meets our criteria for excellence. This is a premier opportunity to secure a high-caliber vehicle that delivers a premium driving experience without the premium price tag. Dependable, polished, and road-ready\u2014this is an investment in quality you can drive with confidence.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. This beauty has been my trusty companion on many road trips and has never let me down. She\u2019s in wonderful shape, runs smooth as silk, and honestly, every time I get behind the wheel, I can't help but smile. She\u2019s got a few tiny signs of being well-loved\u2014just a bit of character, really\u2014but she\u2019s got so many more memories left to make. I\u2019m looking for a good home for her where she'll be appreciated as much as I have. Come take her for a spin and see why I\u2019m so obsessed!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This is a driver\u2019s machine, pure and simple. Featuring a high-revving naturally aspirated powerplant with an optimized torque curve, this unit delivers crisp throttle response through every gear. The suspension geometry has been meticulously dialed in, ensuring the bushings and dampening rates provide flat cornering without sacrificing chassis composure. I\u2019ve personally verified the compression across all cylinders, and the power delivery remains linear right up to the redline. The limited-slip differential provides exceptional bite on exit, and the gear synchronization is buttery smooth. This isn't just a commuter; it's a precision instrument for the enthusiast who values mechanical synergy and a visceral connection to the pavement. Recent fluid analysis confirms the internal health is robust. Ready for its next pilot.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Solid ride. Clean title. Runs perfect. No games. Priced to move today.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine the golden hour sun glinting off the timeless curves of this silver-maned stallion. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a time capsule to an era of effortless elegance. Every mile on the odometer is a story told in the rich, lived-in aroma of its cognac leather interior. The engine hums with a deep, reassuring baritone that promises weekend escapes through winding coastal roads. While it wears the gentle grace of its history, it possesses a spirited heart that yearns for the open road. It\u2019s a machine with a soul, waiting for a driver who understands that true beauty isn't found in a showroom floor shine, but in the character of a legend that has truly lived.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Experience the perfect balance of performance and reliability with this meticulously maintained vehicle. Offering a smooth driving experience and a clean, well-preserved interior, this car represents an outstanding value for the discerning driver. Fully inspected and ready for the road, it combines modern comforts with proven longevity. Don't miss this opportunity to own a premium vehicle at a competitive price point.",
      "price": 32900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty has been my reliable companion and still turns heads every time I take her out for a spin. She\u2019s in really wonderful shape\u2014sure, she\u2019s got a few tiny 'adventure marks' here and there that just show she\u2019s been well-loved, but she runs like a dream and is ready for her next chapter. I\u2019ve taken great care of her, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will appreciate her as much as I do. Come by for a coffee and a test drive; I'd love to show you why this car is so special!",
      "price": 33800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a meticulously sorted E46 M3 that delivers a pure, visceral driving experience. The S54 inline-six remains a masterpiece of engineering, pulling with a linear torque curve and crisp throttle response that only a perfectly timed Vanos system can provide. I have proactively addressed the chassis's structural integrity with a comprehensive subframe reinforcement and overhauled the rod bearings to ensure internal longevity. The suspension geometry has been fine-tuned to minimize unsprung weight, resulting in immediate turn-in and exceptional lateral stability through the apex. The 6-speed manual gearbox is tight, with zero synchro delay, reflecting a drivetrain that has been maintained to the highest mechanical standards. This is a driver-focused machine where the mechanical vitals are prioritized over showroom fluff.",
      "price": 38950.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_8",
